# Azure ML API Configuration
# This file shows the STRUCTURE of environment variables needed
# DO NOT commit your actual credentials to version control!
#
# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file and save as .env (without the .example suffix)
# 2. Fill in your actual values from Azure ML Studio
# 3. .env is in .gitignore and will NOT be committed to git
# 4. Keep your credentials safe - never share your .env file

# Your deployed Azure ML endpoint URL
# Get this from: Azure ML Studio → Endpoints → [Your Endpoint Name] → REST endpoint
API_ENDPOINT=https://eastus2.api.azureml.ms/pipelines/v1.0/subscriptions/...

# Your Azure ML API key for authentication
# Get this from: Azure ML Studio → Endpoints → [Your Endpoint Name] → Keys section
API_KEY=your-api-key-here
